  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to evaluate the efficacy of prophylactic clip application after
      colonoscopic removal for a large pedunculated polyp (&gt; 1cm) in preventing immediate
      postpolypectomy bleeding (IPPB) and delayed postpolypectomy bleeding (DPPB).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
