  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients who have a large pedunculated polyp(&gt;1cm) in the colon

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Age under 20 years

          -  Subjects who are taking anticoagulants

          -  Subjects who have an abnormal coagulogram (platelet count, international normalized
             ratio, or activated partial thromboplastin time)

          -  Subjects who have inflammatory bowel diseases
      </textblock>
